- `ws_client::tests::recv_fragmented` - Receive fragmented message
- `ws_client::tests::ping_pong_auto` - Automatic ping/pong handling
- `ws_client::tests::max_message_size` - Enforce max message size
- `ws_client::tests::close_normal` - Clean close with code 1000

### Cancel-Correctness Tests
- `ws_client::cancel::cancel_during_connect` - Cancel during handshake
- `ws_client::cancel::cancel_during_send` - Cancel mid-send
- `ws_client::cancel::cancel_during_recv` - Cancel while waiting
- `ws_client::cancel::region_close_sends_1001` - Clean close on region close
